 Ahmed Musa and his wife Super Eagles Captain Ahmed Musa have been dragged on social media by some members of the Muslim community who have condemned a photo shared he shared on his social media page. The Nigerian international footballer, shared a loved-up photo of himself and his wife, and in the photo his wife could be seen giving him a kiss on his cheeks. However, some Nigerians have a problem with it and have lashed out at the Super Eagles captain advising him not to post such photo on social media again.